text: Anna Woźniakowska (born 2 March 1982) is a Polish volleyball player. She played at the 2009 Women's European Volleyball Championship, 2008 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2009 FIVB World Grand Prix. She played for Calisia. == References == Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Polish volleyball players
